<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4570763">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4570763/" class="title-link">这书主要还是给学者看的。</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4570763"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1558594/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1558594/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">谈谈</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-01-08"
      class="main-meta">2011-01-08 23:09:30</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4570763_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  老百姓都挺道德的。 儒林外史那就是另外一回事了。 这书是给儒林看的。 儒林自古至今都有共同的特点。 中国今日儒林多看看这书蛮好。 我可不是反智主义。薛涌才反智主义。 反智主义就是红脖子老客了不是？

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 5没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4570763_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4570763_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










